text: Ficus muelleriana is a species of plant in the family Moraceae. It is endemic to Mozambique. It is threatened by habitat loss. ==References== ==Sources== * World Conservation Monitoring Centre 1998. Ficus muelleriana. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 21 August 2007.
